Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:49.97,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord0\shad3\blur3}等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:53.81,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord0\shad3\blur3}出生没多久就到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:22:58.86,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord0\shad3\blur3}虽说这一路上抉择不断
